lso helped the students make paper planes. Both the Airytails team and Apollo Isha Vidhya Niketan students enjoyed themselves in making the paper planes and flying them the farthest, of course!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":45} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://blog.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/blog10.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-45\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The whole school was awed at the enthusiasm of the Airytails – the enthusiasm to kindle the minds of the young pupils to dream to fly!<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","The First Imaginary Take Off With AIRYTAILS.","","inherit","closed","closed","","41-revision-v1","","","2019-04-17 17:14:21","2019-04-17 17:14:21","",41,"http://blog.local/41-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
